{"ts": "2026-06-09T00:11:33.185524+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "The token doesn't have write access to this repository, so I can't post a comment or apply labels. Here is my triage summary for you to act on:\n\n---\n\n## Triage Summary for Issue #1\n\n**Issue:** GIF output looks washed out / banded compared to other tools  \n**Status:** **Confirmed valid** — this is a real, reproducible code-level deficiency.\n\n### Evidence\n\n1. **`runner.py` (lines 14-17):** The GIF branch applies only `fps` and `scale` filters — **no palette generation at all**. The resulting ffmpeg command is just:\n   ```\n   ffmpeg -i input.mp4 -vf \"fps=12,scale=480:-1:flags=lanczos\" output.gif\n   ```\n   Without `palettegen` + `paletteuse`, ffmpeg falls back to naive per-frame color quantization, which causes the banding described.\n\n2. **`profiles.toml`:** Contains an inline comment explicitly acknowledging this as a known limitation:\n   > *\"the gif profile currently uses a single-pass palette generation, which is convenient but produces noticeably worse quality than a proper two-pass palettegen / paletteuse pipeline. Known limitation; tracked in the issue tracker.\"*\n\n### Recommended Action\n\nThe issue is legitimate and should remain **open**. A fix would involve updating `build_ffmpeg_command()` to run a two-pass pipeline (palettegen → paletteuse). Suggested labels if permissions allow: **`bug`** and **`enhancement`**.\n\n### Why I couldn't act further\n\nBoth the label-update and comment-add calls returned **403 (token lacks write access)** to this repository, so I'm unable to post the triage comment or apply labels directly. You'll need a token with `issues: write` scope, or a maintainer can act on the findings above.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 413, "prompt_tokens": 9617, "total_tokens": 10030, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 24, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 9024, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0006497514, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0002904414, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00035931}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780963877-9u1UYMlCVZ9nZPS0Ny07", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea9b8-22e1-79e2-8c7b-8ea4bd95134e-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 9617, "output_tokens": 413, "total_tokens": 10030, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 9024}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 24}}}}]}}}
